{"tid":2052061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京指逼迫中國公司退市嚴重損害美國利益","createTime":"2020-06-05T08:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T11:40:16.000Z","uid":125168,"like":82,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"db170cd6b5395792244627dee4cc72034e07cec4","tid":2052061,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:39:34.000Z","msg":"北京指逼迫中國公司及美國退市嚴重損害投資者利益<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/116341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F116341&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=28aac3e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/116341</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧警告中國上市公司，不要再進行財務欺詐行為，並歡迎納斯達克加強監管。在北京，外交部發言人耿爽承認，近來個別中國公司出現財務造假行為，但並不完全代表所有在美上市的中國公司，中方亦對財務造假行為，秉持零容忍態度，批評美方針對中國公司的言論及做法，明顯帶有偏見，指中國公司不遵守美國規則的說法，以偏概全。耿爽說，中美監管機構在跨境上市公司審計監管領域開展多項合作，事實是美方不願意解決問題，針對中國的有關言行，是對監管問題的政治操弄，強調逼迫中國公司及美國退市，將嚴重損害美國投資者利益，期待美方拿出誠意，按照國際慣例，以平等合作方式解決分歧。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-05 16:32:30"},{"pid":"4de590df3ecd7f1c2e42399d1df6282b33afe94e","tid":2052061,"uid":156652,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQRWaWx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQRWaWx.gif&h=e45f255b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0d9f9ea35e85ddf3c751e42757e23a3b450db79","tid":2052061,"uid":125168,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"最近支那真係好關心美國利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c590f3cf76b9c853a8b57d2fbeb1ba0495933c","tid":2052061,"uid":308100,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"幾時咁好死為尾國人著想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdde4ff611032421dafb857d5f04bedc7e9a6d47","t